團認為事主是自願有性接觸；裁定非禮罪成，只因根據法律，以X的年齡，被告不能以X自願作為辯解理由。"},{"pid":"8242477d8b4107e5270e08a0b1a3dba56a120187","tid":1768699,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:42:40.000Z","msg":"(感謝list on Twitter!) 通過Uyghur Human Rights Policy Act<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9b322a7e9ffd588f75137972144923352f317cb6","tid":1768699,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d05da1b592aa10409b5351b4f22c94b1f30f085b","tid":1768699,"uid":4574,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:15:44.000Z","msg":"以胸襲警陳碧嬌<br />\n少年藏武蘇惠德<br />\n口水判罪香淑嫻<br />\n偷拍無罪彭寶琴<br />\n機場禁制周家明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:07:50.000Z","msg":"點先可以清算呢班垃圾，佢地同綠色曱甴係同一個級數"},{"pid":"51352f723f3527ff2596f044085a8f8e8f43163d","tid":1768699,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:16:37.000Z","msg":"一半高院法官可以永享大灣區榮耀"}]}